				<guid>http://www.scpwiki.com/forum/t-13139822#post-4769077</guid>
				<title>(no title)</title>
				<link>http://www.scpwiki.com/forum/t-13139822/scp-4573#post-4769077</link>
				<description></description>
				<pubDate>Mon, 07 Sep 2020 05:19:44 +0000</pubDate>
				<wikidot:authorName>Vincent Van Gone</wikidot:authorName>				<wikidot:authorUserId>4874299</wikidot:authorUserId>				<content:encoded>
					<![CDATA[
						 <p>The general concept of the Foundation somehow committing piracy seems interesting, but it doesn't work with something as boring as this. I think it would be interesting to see you rework that general concept to be paired with something which can stand on its own and is intriguing without that added element.</p> <p>After I make this comment I'll likely go in and correct a few spelling errors I saw throughout.</p> 
				 	]]>
				</content:encoded>							</item>
					<item>
				<guid>http://www.scpwiki.com/forum/t-13139822#post-4551573</guid>
				<title>(no title)</title>
				<link>http://www.scpwiki.com/forum/t-13139822/scp-4573#post-4551573</link>
				<description></description>
