				<wikidot:authorName>Pythy</wikidot:authorName>				<wikidot:authorUserId>1585502</wikidot:authorUserId>				<content:encoded>
					<![CDATA[
						 <p>Biology note: not all animals have brains, and hence brain waves. For instance, starfish have no brains. It would probably be a good idea to restrict the species that this affects to just Chordata or to vertebrates. Or all species with brains, for that matter.</p> 
				 	]]>
				</content:encoded>							</item>
